cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image synthesis and patch distribution. It could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category as it proposes a new type of Generative Adversarial Network. Additionally, it could be categorized under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) as it involves the creation of new images. The Graphics (cs.GR) and Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories are also possible as they deal with image manipulation and generation.
